  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nIt's hard to get a failed transaction hash.\r\n\r\nTruffle v5 supports the [EventEmitter interface for contract methods](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/releases/tag/v5.0.0-beta.0#methods-eventemitter), which works for successful transactions, but not for failed transactions. (Possibly a timing issue with Ganache instamine)\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nDefine a Solidity file\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\npragma solidity ^0.4.24;\r\n\r\ncontract Reverts {\r\n  bool failed;\r\n\r\n  function succeed() public {\r\n    failed = false;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  function fail() public {\r\n    failed = true;\r\n    revert(\"test-failure\");\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen open `truffle develop` and run the commands:\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nconst reverts = await Reverts.new()\r\nreverts.succeed().on('transactionHash', console.log)\r\nreverts.fail().on('transactionHash', console.log)\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\n`truffle(develop)> reverts.succeed().on('transactionHash', console.log)`:\r\n```\r\n0xbaf4d557c0154210ec2dc4ebbb9d2be333e5d8a5ac0eab64fc30e222c33100e7\r\n{ tx: '0xbaf4d557c0154210ec2dc4ebbb9d2be333e5d8a5ac0eab64fc30e222c33100e7',\r\n  receipt:\r\n   { transactionHash: '0xbaf4d557c0154210ec2dc4ebbb9d2be333e5d8a5ac0eab64fc30e222c33100e7',\r\n     transactionIndex: 0,\r\n     blockHash: '0xde7dad89752adf221ac77abe60677c5b170d80fc043fe5409194112e84e36e6b',\r\n     blockNumber: 6,\r\n     gasUsed: 26694,\r\n     cumulativeGasUsed: 26694,\r\n     contractAddress: null,\r\n     logs: [],\r\n     status: true,\r\n     logsBloom: '' },\r\n  logs: [] }\r\n```\r\n\r\n`truffle(develop)> reverts.fail().on('transactionHash', console.log)`\r\n```\r\n0xbaf4d557c0154210ec2dc4ebbb9d2be333e5d8a5ac0eab64fc30e222c33100e7\r\nError:  ... exception message ...\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Actual Behavior\r\n\r\nSuccessful case works but failure case does not:\r\n\r\n```\r\ntruffle(develop)> reverts.fail().on('transactionHash', console.log)\r\nError: Returned error: VM Exception while processing transaction: revert test-failure -- Reason given: test-failure.\r\n  ...\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Ethereum client: truffle-develop\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.0.0-beta.1\r\n",
